    public static class NavigationManager.RoadView

        public void setOrientation(NavigationManager.RoadView.Orientation orientation)
        Sets the orientation for NavigationManager.MapUpdateMode.ROADVIEW and NavigationManager.MapUpdateMode.ROADVIEW_NOZOOM. This method is only effective after the navigation has started running, otherwise NavigationManager.RoadView.Orientation.DYNAMIC is used by default.
